                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/opinion">OPINION</a></span></div>

                <h1>It doesn&#039;t get better</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/monday-monday">Monday Monday</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">April 15, 2013 | 3:23am EDT</span>
